AA IT belongs to the ActionAid Federation working with over 15 million  people in 45 countries worldwide. Through ActionAid International it is  a member of several non-profit networks and confederations, including at EU level the Concord and the Eurodad Networks.&#xd;
&#xd;
AA Italy belongs also to several Italian Networks such as: &#xd;
- "Alleanza contro La Povertà/ Alliance against poverty" aimed at promoting innovative measures to fight against social exclusion, &#xd;
- "Italia Sveglia /Italy Wake Up" fostering social innovation in governance relationships, &#xd;
- "Agire/Act" intended to facilitate fundraising &amp; interventions in post emergency situations, &#xd;
- "CINI" the most relevant International Network of Italian NGO &#xd;
- "Forum Terzo Settore /Third Sector Forum"- it includes more than 14 millions citizens via associations and groups of the CSOs &#xd;
- CPDE - CSO Partnership for effective development cooperation, appointing the CSO delegate for the Global Partnership for Effective Development Cooperation.
